4743605", "title": "PG&E's New Convertible Preferred Offers Dual Benefit", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1331029618/image_1331029618.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Bakersfield, California\" data-id=\"1331029618\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1331029618/image_1331029618.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1331029618/image_1331029618.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1331029618/image_1331029618.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1331029618/image_1331029618.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1331029618/image_1331029618.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1331029618/image_1331029618.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1331029618/image_1331029618.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1331029618/image_1331029618.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">MattGush</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>PG&amp;E Corp. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PCG\" title=\"PG&amp;E Corporation\">PCG</a></span>) last week <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4357640-pge-prices-235b-offering-stock-up\">raised a net $2.35 billion</a> by offering common shares priced at $20.35 and issuing 32.2 million shares of a new preferred series at $50 a share. Some of the proceeds will be used to</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1331029618/image_1331029618.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743605-pg-and-e-new-convertible-preferred-offers-dual-benefit", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 19:14:02"}, {"id": "4743613", "title": "A Sluggish Year Ahead For Carbon Demand", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/96390216/image_96390216.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Coal Miners With Clipboard\" data-id=\"96390216\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1153px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/96390216/image_96390216.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/96390216/image_96390216.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/96390216/image_96390216.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/96390216/image_96390216.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/96390216/image_96390216.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/96390216/image_96390216.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/96390216/image_96390216.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/96390216/image_96390216.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Monty Rakusen</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By <a href=\"https://think.ing.com/author/warren-patterson/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Warren Patterson</a></em></p> <h2>Weak demand and strong supply</h2> <p>EU Allowances (EUAs) have been under pressure for much of the year. Weak industrial production and strong renewables output have weighed on demand for EUAs over the year. This saw prices trading down to</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/96390216/image_96390216.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743613-sluggish-year-ahead-carbon-demand", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 19:10:00"}, {"id": "4743599", "title": "UiPath: AI And The Path To More Cash Flow", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183301265/image_2183301265.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Friendly cute cartoon robot - 3d render. Technology concept.\" data-id=\"2183301265\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183301265/image_2183301265.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183301265/image_2183301265.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183301265/image_2183301265.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183301265/image_2183301265.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183301265/image_2183301265.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183301265/image_2183301265.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183301265/image_2183301265.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183301265/image_2183301265.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">NESSDesign/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>UiPath Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PATH\" title=\"UiPath Inc.\">PATH</a></span>) delivered fiscal <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4368051-uipath-non-gaap-eps-of-0_11-beats-0_04-revenue-of-354_65m-beats-6_93m\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4368051-uipath-non-gaap-eps-of-0_11-beats-0_04-revenue-of-354_65m-beats-6_93m\" target=\"_blank\">Q3 2025 earnings</a> that were a mixed bag. On the one hand, the business is clearly pulling every lever available to bring in strong free cash flow.</p> <p>While on the other hand, the business</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183301265/image_2183301265.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743599-uipath-ai-and-the-path-to-more-cash-flow", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 18:57:00"}, {"id": "4743618", "title": "Allspring Special Large Cap Value Fund Q3 2024 Commentary", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442855295/image_1442855295.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Man hand stacked coins\" data-id=\"1442855295\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"865px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442855295/image_1442855295.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442855295/image_1442855295.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442855295/image_1442855295.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442855295/image_1442855295.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com